ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd857728fdfa8cd297184b7463bca25b3056981","tid":1697400,"uid":76363,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:14:30.000Z","msg":"換樓都係貴買貴賣<br />\n平買平賣<br />\n咩時候換有咁大關係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:29:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:42:57.000Z","msg":"我都係咁話<br />\n又要岩價賣 又要睇岩<br />\n寧願用心機睇樓 好過等樓價跌"},{"pid":"73290e93c878e7f1a204d0fe77e358075df81a9c","tid":1697400,"uid":281825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"買鐵路上蓋盤 抗跌能力都高啲"},{"pid":"e10190dc52a106dbe90053f4a0f158bf5aa33a0e","tid":1697400,"uid":45290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"二手樓價指數創15周最大升幅　中原指樓市調整結束<br />\n<br />\n反映本港二手樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數(CCL)升至179.4，按星期升0.22%，創15個星期以來最大升幅。<br />\n<br />\n中原表示，政府上調按揭保險樓價上限，樓市氣氛好轉，CCL、大型屋苑領先指數、中小型單位指數齊升，結束10星期齊跌走勢，確認樓市調整結束。<br />\n<br />\n中小型單位按星期升0.27%，升幅是15個星期以來最大，大型單位則微跌0.03%，中原指豪宅近4星期窄幅徘徊，等待向上突破。<br />\n<br />\n分區樓價個別發展，新界西升幅最大，按星期升約1.4%，帶動大市止跌回升。港島及九龍升近0.3%或以上，新界東則跌約0.8%，指數創29個星期新低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490803-20191108.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490803-20191108.htm&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=18c3c54c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490803-20191108.htm&h=363cf78c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490803-20191108.htm</a>"},{"pid":"52ca617dc8122a0e5aefe09c6282bab582915bbe","tid":1697400,"uid":208663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"明年發生咩事你都知 你有水晶球？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid